game.name: Tangled Tower Cupcake
game.description:
Hey ladies! Have you ever watched a popular movie called Tangled? If you saw it and enjoyed a lot, then you would definitely love to learn how to create your own nice towers in cupcake form. You do not have an idea who delicious would they be if cooked perfectly. Rapunzel is a very kind-hearted, brave and beautiful character and, for this reason, this brand new cooking game is dedicated to her. The process is quite simple and easy to learn for anyone and you will be able to create a fantastic recipe in the end. 

Rapunzel likes this recipe very much, so she will also be there to provide you with the useful tricks and tips of the preparation part. Follow all the steps one-by-one and have the best time while preparing this scrumptious recipe. Start this brand new cooking game with mixing vanilla extract, some sugar and butter into a bowl. Take another bowl and mix some flour and baking powder into it. Now blend all the mixtures together including some flavoured milk, as per your taste. Collect some muffin cups and pour the batter into them. 

Place them in a special tray, which you will have to put in the oven to bake the muffins for a while. Leave them for getting them cooled. Meanwhile you can construct the rest of the towers. Collect a stick and put it standing up. Once it is done, get ready to insert some pecan rolls in it on top of the other. Inside a smaller stripped muffin cap, use a pecan roll and put some perfectly baked fresh muffins on the top of it. Use a waffle cone and dip it perfectly into the nicely prepared purple melted candy. Complete your recipe by placing it on top of your favorite cupcake tower. Use the green topping to decorate your dessert. Have fun kids!
